===Noun===
'''forget-me-not''' (''plural'' '''[[forget-me-nots]]''')

# A [[genus]] of [[flower]]ing [[plant]]s of the [[genus]] ''Myosotis'', mostly with a [[small]] 5-petalled [[blue]] [[flower]].

